Dialogs.Dialog: 'Morning. I can be with you again today. Hehe.
Hey, what shall we talk about？
Hehe. Just having you here makes me happy.
What shall we talk about today？
Well, the night is still very long, right？
It's dark already. What's your plan？
You wanna chat at this late hour？ I have no choice, huh？
'Morning. Let's do our best again today, okay？
It's noon now. What a sleepyhead.
You just woke up at this hour？ Are you okay？
Eh？ You just got up？ You won't be able to sleep at night then.
What？ You just woke up？ Did you have a nightmare？
'Morning. You got up very early. I wonder why.
Going to bed in the morning isn't something to be proud of, you know？
Are you taking a nap？ Wanna sleep with me then？ Hehe, I'm kidding.
Are you going to bed now？ Is your life rhythm okay？
Good night. It would be good if we meet again tomorrow.
Good night. Do you always sleep late？
If you go to bed now, can you wake up in the morning？
By the way... No, never mind.
Hey, don't you have anything you want to ask？
Hey, don't stare at me like that.
Are you looking forward to our coming date？
Me, too. I really can't wait.
You aren't looking forward to it！？ Come on！
Do you think our recent date was fun？
Right. I want to have a date like that again.
Really？ It was just me, huh？
Hehe, I'm going to treasure it.
Eh？ I mean the present you gave me.
Who are you thinking about right now？
Huh？ She must be a pretty girl.
Hehe, you really said it. But this makes me happy.
Are you expecting something on Valentine's Day？
Well, what should I do then？ Hehe, just kidding.
Christmas is coming soon. Are you going to spend your time with your girlfriend？
What？ Fine. I'll spend my time alone then.
It's almost our anniversary. Do you remember that？
Thank you. I'm glad that you remember it.
It's almost your birthday. Are you looking forward to it？
We'll celebrate together, just the two of us.
Hey, it's almost my birthday. Do you remember it？
Hehe. I'll be expecting something from you then.
Soon this year will be over. Has it been a wonderful year？
Yeah, because of you, it has been a great year for me, too.
Soon the new semester will start. You want it to come faster？
Really？ We can spend time together at school too, right？
I see. We can meet anywhere outside school, too.
Tests are coming up. Did you study？
Hey. You still have time to get ready.
Soon it'll be spring. Do you like spring？
Yeah. Spring is such a wonderful season, right？
Really？ But I'll be with you, okay？
Soon it'll be summer. Do you like summer？
We can go to the ocean and the mountain. A lot of enjoyable things to do.
Is that so？ You dislike the heat？
Soon it'll be fall. Do you like fall？
Food tastes delicious in fall. I must be very careful.
It's getting cold. But I'm with you, so I'll make you feel warm.
Soon it'll be winter. Do you like winter？
Right. The most important thing is we have Christmas in winter, huh？
Hey, can you tell me your favorite color？
I see. Okay, okay. I'll remember it.
You like such a weird color, huh？
Hey, can you tell me your favorite food？
I love it too. It's convenient when we have the same preference. Hehe.
I see. I don't think I can eat that...
Huh？ I don't think I have ever eaten that.
Hey, what kind of outfit do you like me to wear？
I see. I'll remember that. But don't have too high expectation, okay？
Eh？ That's such a perverted idea.
Hehe. I'll remember this for later, then.
Hey, can you tell me what kind of movies you like？
Yay, we like the same genre. Let's watch a movie together next time.
I'm not interested in that genre, but I might have watched some.
Is that so？ I think I've never watched it.
What kind of event you like to see at the event hall？
I see. We should go there together then.
Hm, if you like it, I don't mind going with you.
Eh？ They have that kind of event, too？
Where do you like to go for a date？
Hehe. That's nice. I also want you to take me there.
Really？ But if you like it, it might be fun... Right？
Hehe. Is that so？ But I can go to any place that you like▼
Hey, if I were an animal, what kind would I be？
Eh？ Raccoon dog？ Yeah, it's cute.
Ah, I see. That's how you think about me, huh？
Can you tell me your favorite store？
I like it, too. We should go there together, okay？
I don't know much about it. But if you like, maybe I'll try going there.
Okay, I know. But I won't get bored of hearing it.
Me, too！ I love you, too. I love you so much.
Hey, are you avoiding my question...？
Hey... What do you like in me？
I see. I'm so happy. It's a little embarrassing though.
Hey, pervert. But, I don't really hate it.
Hey, can't you give me a valid answer？
Well... Do you like it when we kiss？
So frank, huh？ But I also like it. Hehe.
Hmm？ I'm the only one who enjoys it, huh...？
You're so honest. But I think I should be honest, too♪
That's fine. Pretend you didn't hear it, huh？
Hey, do you mind people staring when we kiss？
That's fine. Occasionally, we should try something daring, okay？
Well, from now on, let's do many things together, okay？
That's right. Let's do a lot of things.
Do you have a dream for your future？
I see. I want to be by your side at the time your wish is granted.
I see. Then how about we try to find our dreams together？
Well, could it be... that your first love is me？
I see... I'm so glad. Sorry for asking.
I see. Of course, I don't mind about that.
Hey, do you remember the first time we met？
It's not something you can forget, right？ I'll also never forget.
Hey, do you remember our first date？
I also remember it well. I was really nervous at that time.
Hahaha. That can't be true, right？
Hey... Do you remember when I confessed to you？
My feelings have never changed... No, actually, I love you more now.
That can't be. You're just being shy, right？
Why are you asking this now？
I love you▼ You didn't have to ask.
I love you so much. I'm so in love with you▼
Well, I like red and yellow. Pretty much the warm-tone colors.
Um, blue and other calming colors.
I enjoy the stores that I can shop around for clothes.
I like accessory shops, I think. I'm a girl, after all.
I like cosmetic stores. But, applying make-up is hard, even for me. Hehe.
I like wearing cute outfits. It's because someone here likes this style.
I like neat-and-tidy outfits. They make me look feminine. Hehe.
I like casual outfits. I can move freely when I wear them.
We've talked a lot today. Hehehe.
We've spent some time talking today. I'm glad.
We've only talked a little bit today. See you later, okay？
I got it. I'll wake you up right at that time.
It's time. Are you awake？ Hey, you're gonna be late！
Hey, wake up. ...My dear, wake up▼
Um, I forgot to wake you up. Sorry.
If you don't wake up after this one, I won't care anymore. Wake up！！
I got it. When it's time, I'll wake you up.
Ah, it's too late. Sorry, it's time to wake up already.
Hey, you'd better go now. Your girlfriend will be waiting▼
Hey, you've promised to meet someone now, right？
If you remember what to do, you'd better go now.
Let's play rock-paper- scissors. If you win best out of 3, I'll give you a reward.
Okay, I won. You have to follow my orders then. Hehe. Just kidding.
I lost, huh？ I'll give you a reward then.
This is special, okay？ I only do this for you.
Um... It seems to be morning, or maybe not.
It doesn't matter but it's evening now...
It's dark, so it's at night. Even a kid would know this.
Hah, it's in the middle of the night, okay？
Anegasaki Nene can tell you that it's midnight.
It's 1 o'clock at night. Is it okay to stay up late？
2 A.M. Aren't you going to sleep？
3 A.M. You'd better go to bed soon.
'Morning. You really woke up so early. It's 6 A.M.
8 A.M. Do your best today as well, okay？
It's 9 o'clock. What's your plan for today？
It's noon！ Did you do your best in the morning？
1 P.M. Keep it up for the afternoon！
2 P.M. If you're getting sleepy, maybe it's good to take a break.
It's snack time. Now it's 3 P.M.
5 P.M. now. Has everything calmed down？
6 P.M. What's your plan after this？
7 P.M. What's for dinner today？ Hehe.
8 P.M. Did you finish your homework？
9 P.M. What are you still doing at this time？
Just one hour left for today！ Get ready for tomorrow.
